  "description": "A sun-dappled stream scene. Clear, shallow water flows over a rocky bed, creating ripples and reflections of the surrounding foliage. A splash of water disrupts the surface, suggesting movement or an object entering the water. Lush green vegetation, including ferns and trees, lines the banks, creating a vibrant and natural environment. The lighting is soft and diffused, with sunlight filtering through the trees, enhancing the serene atmosphere. The streambed appears rocky and uneven. The focus is on the water\u2019s surface and the play of light and shadow.",
